snippet.textDisplay:
A LETTER TO TRUMP SUPPORTERS.

The Trump slogan of “ Make America Great Again” is arguably the most effective slogan ever in politics.

It’s aspirational.
All Americans want their country to be great
It promises hope.

BUT! It can never work unless it’s tied to the taxation system that made America great in the first place!

Donald Trump is on record saying the he believes America was great in the late forties and fifties...O.K. let’s agree with him.

The driving force that created American greatness was taxation rates as high as 91%

Put simply you can’t drive a car with no motor...from the outside the cars all shinny and new, the salesman’s telling how great it will be and the freedom it will offer you and how much fun it will be to own.

But! He didn’t tell you it doesn’t have a motor.

THINK ABOUT IT....MAGA is just a slogan without a motor.
